(11, 0, 'HDFC Property Loan | Jaidev property', 'HDFC Property Loan', 'HDFC Property Loan', '', 5, 'Jaidev', '02/04/2013', '1', '<div class="h1">\r\n<h1>HDFC Property Loan</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="aj">\r\n<p class="fr pl10px"><img style="float: right;" title="HDFC Property Loan" src="http://catalog.wlimg.com/3/26881/small-images/hdfc-property-loan-9665.jpg" alt="HDFC Property Loan" width="152" height="156" /></p>\r\n<h2>HDFC Property Loan</h2>\r\n<p>Pune Property Times provides the services of a Property Loan Consultant in Pune &amp; Pimpri Chinchwad area. Our Property Loan Consultant offers the best advice on different property loans. We assist our clients in obtaining all types of property loan. Loan taking is a very tedious process as a lot of verifications are involved. This is because banks are on their guard all the time as a lot of fraud and deception is practiced these days.</p>\r\n<p>The entire loan taking procedure becomes simple and hassle-free with our involvement. We have tied up with a reputed bank like HDFC Bank Property loans of residential loan / commercial loan, over the years have built a great working relationship with it. As far as loan taking goes, our reputation has a leading real estate agent has always stood by us in good stead and loans becomes easily accessible with our association with the process of taking loans.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<form action="http://www.punepropertytimes.com/send-inquiry1.htm" method="post" name="products_form" enctype="multipart/form-data">\r\n<p class="ac"><a class="buttonBig c10px dib p10px20px" title="Send Inquiry" href="http://jaidevlandmarks.com/admin/insert/">Send Inquiry</a></p>\r\n</form>', 9, '0'),
