(6, '24K Glitterati - Pune', 'Kolte Patil Developers', '', '1', 'Residential Property', 'Residential', ' Pimple Nilakh', '<div class="aj">\r\n<p>24K is a niche brand by Kolte-Patil Developers Ltd. It offers finest homes, extraordinary in terms of location, engineering, designing and amenities.&nbsp;<br /><br />24K Glitterati has exclusive, river-facing homes starting from 2,000 sft going all the way up to 6,000 sft. 5 towers offer 3 and 4 bedroom super luxurious apartments, garden homes and 5 bedroom duplex penthouses with terrace deck, garden and a private pool.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 'http://manage.goldenlandmarks.net/admin/upload/uploaded-files/parkroyale-layoutplan1.jpg', '', '<p><strong>Lifestyle<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>The only thing you need to take care of is unannounced guests.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You can start living here the moment you get the keys. Or rather, the smart card. From exclusive fittings to white goods, we have taken care of everything. Your home comes loaded with every imaginable amenity and a few unimaginable ones too.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Smart Homes<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>24k homes are smarter than most people.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>All 24k homes feature proprietary, cutting edge automation and electronic systems designed for 24k. You can adjust AC temperature, raise or lower the curtains, see who&rsquo;s r inging the bell, switch-on or switch-off the lights, select who will enter your home or call the elevator, all while you are sitting on the couch. You still have to press a few buttons, but we are working on that.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Green Homes<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>We Love the Colour Green.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We care for nature and it&rsquo;s reflected in the way we build our projects. We don&rsquo;t just use nature friendly materials but also make sure that this nature friendliness is sustainable forever.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Service<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Only the nature of our products is understated.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rest everything is bold and in Black &amp; White. All permissions are taken beforehand and every certificate is provided on time. Customer service is taken to a new level with property management, facility management and what not. Because once you are a 24k customer, you can expect everything 24k.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Community<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>24k A prefix revered highly and lusted after.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We are very selective about everything related to 24k - from choosing the right location to even selecting the customers. Not just residential, but retail and commercial buyers are also handpicked. It&rsquo;s a community for evolved people. And, we love to keep it that way.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Architecture<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Air needs Space.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Design Thinking is what we do. Every square inch in a 24k home has a reason to be there. Space division, selecting amenities or integrating innovative solutions, everything is thought thorough and then designed. The objective is to free-up as much space as possible, to let you have your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Engineering<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Very few have a spine like this.</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>24k projects a rebuilt like nothing else you&rsquo;ve seen. Every stage of material selection, construction and finishing is carefully planned and executed to give you a home that will stay new for a lifetime. A claim very few can make. But after all, not everyone is 24k.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>GARDEN HOMES</strong></p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Open On 3 Sides, Gardens On 3 Sides.<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Your living room extends into a garden which extends into a podium landscape which overlooks the river side green scape. Further, there are private terraces too, for you to enjoy the view.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>3 and 4 BHK apartments with private, fenced gardens from 1000 SFT - 1500 SFT.</li>\r\n<li>Landscaped to your taste and ideas by our designers</li>\r\n<li>Living room with terrace deck</li>\r\n<li>Master bedroom with terrace/sun deck and walk-in-wardrobe</li>\r\n<li>Designer entrance lobby with attached box area</li>\r\n<li>Finest Italian marble flooring for the living and dining area</li>\r\n<li>Staff room</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><br />TERRACE APARTMENTS</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><br />3 &amp; 4 bedroom apartments</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>3 and 4 BHK apartments with private, fenced gardens from 1000 SFT - 1500 SFT.</li>\r\n<li>Landscaped to your taste and ideas by our designers</li>\r\n<li>Living room with terrace deck</li>\r\n<li>Master bedroom with terrace/sun deck and walk-in-wardrobe</li>\r\n<li>Designer entrance lobby with attached box area</li>\r\n<li>Finest Italian marble flooring for the living and dining area</li>\r\n<li>Staff room</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Master Bedroom</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Terrace/Sun deck</li>\r\n<li>Walk-in-wardrobe</li>\r\n<li>Laminated wooden flooring</li>\r\n<li>(Vitrified flooring in other bedrooms)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Kitchen</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stylish modular kitchen with chimney and hob</li>\r\n<li>Optimum space utilization and an eye for ergonomics</li>\r\n<li>Granite-top kitchen platform</li>\r\n<li>Scratch free S.S. sink with drain-board</li>\r\n<li>Water purifier</li>\r\n<li>Reticulated piped gas system</li>\r\n<li>Utility space with provision for washing machine</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><br />PENTHOUSE<br /><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>These penthouses have the best of what 24k has to offer. Be it design, amenities or just sheer space, they make everything else pale in comparison.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Duplex Penthouse</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Majestic 5 bedroom duplex penthouses</li>\r\n<li>Double height living room with an attached terrace</li>\r\n<li>Majestic entrance lobby at the lower level</li>\r\n<li>Rooftop terrace</li>\r\n<li>Private Pool</li>\r\n<li>Jacuzzi</li>\r\n<li>Swimming pool</li>\r\n<li>Party/meditation/sun deck</li>\r\n<li>Landscaped garden</li>\r\n<li>Bar counter attached to the living-dining area</li>\r\n<li>Two lavish master suites</li>\r\n<li>100% D.G. back-up</li>\r\n<li>Italian marble/wooden/vitrified flooring</li>\r\n<li>Fully air-conditioned (except in staff and washrooms)</li>\r\n<li>Smart home technology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Jacuzzi Washroom</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bath tub with whirlpool (only for master bedroom)</li>\r\n<li>Exquisite chrome plated Hansgrohe / equivalent make fittings and fixtures</li>\r\n<li>Premium range Duravit / Roca/ equivalent make sanitary-ware</li>\r\n<li>Designer Dado</li>\r\n<li>Vitrified flooring</li>\r\n<li>Italian marble counter top wash basin</li>\r\n<li>Glass enclosed shower</li>\r\n<li>Water heater in all bathrooms</li>\r\n<li>Concealed corrosion resistant plumbing</li>\r\n<li>Exclusive bathrooms with premium sanitary-ware fixtures</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '', '', '<p>---</p>', '<p class="mb10px"><strong>Jaidev Landmarks</strong></p>\r\n<p class="mb10px"><strong>Address :</strong>&nbsp;Park Street, Nr Mahindra Woods, Hinjewadi Aundh Wakad Road, Wakad, Pune, Maharashtra, India</p>\r\n<p class="mb10px"><strong>Mobile :&nbsp;</strong>+91- 9881331689, 9881502939</p>\r\n<p class="mb10px"><strong>E-mail :</strong>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:collecturkey@gmail.com">collecturkey@gmail.com</a></p>', 4, '1');

